The unidentified ship falls from the sky and lands in the sourthern 
Unitied States. None of the Maximals move from the wreakage. Though 
before they went down the commander pressed a button sending a code 
red warning to all the robots with in a 500 mile circle of the ship.
"S.O.S. ship going down. Need help."

-------------------------------------
--Grimlock--
Grimlock hears the warning inside the Ark and warns Liono. 
"Liono a Maximal ship has enter the atmosphere, it sending a distrast 
call. I am going to see what the problem is."

Grimlock quickly transforms into robot mode and runs toward the 
falling ship.
